(79,"Creamy Mushroom and Goat Cheese Pasta","A savory pasta dish featuring spaghetti with a creamy mushroom and goat cheese sauce, flavored with shallots, garlic, and red pepper flakes.","00:10:00","00:20:00","4","medium","[\"Bring a large pot of salted water to a boil. Add spaghetti and cook until al dente.\", \"In a large pan, melt butter and olive oil. Add shallot, garlic, and red pepper flakes and sauté for 2-3 minutes on low/medium heat.\", \"Add mushrooms and sauté for another 1-2 minutes until mushrooms get soft.\", \"Add heavy cream and bring to a light boil for about 2 minutes, until slightly reduced.\", \"Add goat cheese and mix until combined.\", \"Add parmesan cheese and mix until combined. If the sauce is thick, it will be thinned out with pasta water.\", \"Taste for salt and pepper. Adjust if necessary.\", \"Add cooked spaghetti, adding pasta water as needed to achieve desired consistency.\", \"Top with fresh basil and serve immediately.\"]","2024-01-16 01:13:02","ca49ccb4-7cf0-4477-8f3f-90371e737b38","null","null","2024-01-16 01:13:02","[{\"id\": 0, \"name\": \"spaghetti\", \"unit\": \"Gram\", \"amount\": \"400\"}, {\"id\": 1, \"name\": \"garlic and herb butter\", \"unit\": \"cup\", \"amount\": \"1/4\"}, {\"id\": 2, \"name\": \"goat cheese\", \"unit\": \"Gram\", \"amount\": \"140\"}, {\"id\": 3, \"name\": \"olive oil\", \"unit\": \"Tablespoon\", \"amount\": \"2\"}, {\"id\": 4, \"name\": \"shallot, chopped fine\", \"unit\": \"whole\", \"amount\": \"1\"}, {\"id\": 5, \"name\": \"garlic, chopped fine\", \"unit\": \"clove\", \"amount\": \"3\"}, {\"id\": 6, \"name\": \"red pepper flakes\", \"unit\": \"Teaspoon\", \"amount\": \"1/4\"}, {\"id\": 7, \"name\": \"heavy whipping cream\", \"unit\": \"cup\", \"amount\": \"1\"}, {\"id\": 8, \"name\": \"mushrooms, roughly chopped\", \"unit\": \"cup\", \"amount\": \"2\"}, {\"id\": 9, \"name\": \"parmesan cheese, grated\", \"unit\": \"cup\", \"amount\": \"1\"}, {\"id\": 10, \"name\": \"reserved pasta water\", \"unit\"