(80,"Creamy Tomato Soup","A warm and comforting creamy tomato soup made with diced tomatoes, green onions, and a touch of sugar, best served with crackers.","00:05:00","00:15:00","2","easy","[\"Place the green onions on the cutting board and cut off the root end with a sharp knife. Peel away the outer layer of skin. Cut the white part and about 2 inches of the green into thin slices and set aside.\", \"Open the can of tomatoes with the can opener and pour the contents into the container of the blender. Add the chicken broth, green onions, milk, sugar, 1/2 teaspoon salt, and a pinch of pepper. Put the lid securely on the blender and blend until very smooth.\", \"Pour the contents of the blender into the medium saucepan and set the pan over high heat. Bring the soup to a boil, reduce the heat to low, and simmer, stirring frequently with a wooden spoon, until the soup thickens, about 15 minutes.\", \"Carefully remove the saucepan from the heat. Taste the soup and add more salt or pepper if needed. Ladle the soup into bowls or mugs and serve immediately with crackers.\"]","2024-01-16 23:34:01","ca49ccb4-7cf0-4477-8f3f-90371e737b38","null","null","2024-01-16 23:34:01","[{\"id\": 0, \"name\": \"small green (spring) onions\", \"unit\": \"whole\", \"amount\": \"3\"}, {\"id\": 1, \"name\": \"can diced tomatoes\", \"unit\": \"Ounce\", \"amount\": \"14.5\"}, {\"id\": 2, \"name\": \"chicken broth\", \"unit\": \"cup\", \"amount\": \"1\"}, {\"id\": 3, \"name\": \"milk\", \"unit\": \"cup\", \"amount\": \"1/4\"}, {\"id\": 4, \"name\": \"sugar\", \"unit\": \"Teaspoon\", \"amount\": \"1\"}, {\"id\": 5, \"name\": \"salt and pepper\", \"unit\": \"whole\", \"amount\": \"to taste\"}]",0),
(81,"Favorite Grilled Cheese Sandwich","A gourmet grilled cheese sandwich featuring whole grain sourdough, sharp cheddar, Dijon mustard, and green onions. Cooked to golden perfection on a stovetop.","00:05:00","00:10:00","1","easy","[\"Spread Dijon mustard lightly across one side of one slice of bread.\", \"Stir the green onion into the grated cheese, and set aside.\", \"Melt 1 teaspoon butter in a skillet over medium heat. Place the slice of bread with mustard in the skillet, mustard side up.\", \"Top with the oniony cheese. Cover with the second slice of bread. Cover the skillet with a lid and cook until the bread is golden on the underside.\", \"Remove the sandwich, add another pat of butter to the skillet. Carefully flip the sandwich to cook on the other side until golden and the cheese has melted.\", \"Optional: For a cheesy crust, sprinkle additional cheese in the pan, and flip the sandwich onto the cheese. Cook until the sizzle stops and a few seconds longer.\", \"Let the sandwich cool for a minute, cut in half with a serrated knife, and serve warm.\"]","2024-01-16 23:37:54","ca49ccb4-7cf0-4477-8f3f-90371e737b38","null","null","2024-01-16 23:37:54","[{\"id\": 0, \"name\": \"whole grain sourdough bread\", \"unit\": \"slice\", \"amount\": \"2\"}, {\"id\": 1, \"name\": \"Dijon mustard\", \"unit\": \"Teaspoon\", \"amount\": \"1 1/2\"}, {\"id\": 2, \"name\": \"sharp cheddar cheese, freshly grated\", \"unit\": \"cup\", \"amount\": \"1\"}, {\"id\": 3, \"name\": \"green onion, chopped, green parts only\", \"unit\": \"Teaspoon\", \"amount\": \"2\"}, {\"id\": 4, \"name\": \"unsalted butter\", \"unit\": \"Teaspoon\", \"amount\": \"2\"}]",0),
(82,"Best Chocolate Chip Cookies","These chocolate chip cookies are soft and gooey on the inside, crisp and chewy on the outside, mixed by hand and ready in 30 minutes with no chill time.","00:15:00","00:15:00","9","easy","[\"Preheat the oven to 350F (175C) and line a large baking sheet with parchment paper.\", \"Whisk together flour, baking soda, baking powder, and salt in a medium sized bowl. Set aside.\", \"In a large bowl, whisk together melted and cooled butter, brown sugar, and granulated sugar for 1-2 minutes until paste-like.\", \"Whisk in the egg and vanilla until smooth.\", \"Fold in dry ingredients with a rubber spatula, leaving a few streaks of flour. Add chocolate chips and fold until evenly distributed and no flour streaks remain.\", \"Scoop 5 large cookies onto the baking sheet with a 2oz cookie scoop or 1/4 cup measure and bake for 12-15 minutes. For smaller cookies, scoop 6 and bake for 10-12 minutes.\", \"Cookies are done when edges are golden but centers are pale and puffed. If they spread too much, nudge in the sides with a fork immediately after baking.\", \"Top fresh cookies with extra chocolate chips and a sprinkle of sea salt.\", \"Transfer to a cooling rack and cool for about 20 minutes before serving.\"]","2024-01-24 01:24:36","ca49ccb4-7cf0-4477-8f3f-90371e737b38","null","null","2024-02-09 09:38:25","[{\"id\": 0, \"name\": \"all-purpose flour\", \"unit\": \"cup\", \"amount\": \"1 1/4\"}, {\"id\": 1, \"name\": \"baking soda\", \"unit\": \"Teaspoon\", \"amount\": \"1/2\"}, {\"id\": 2, \"name\": \"baking powder\", \"unit\": \"Teaspoon\", \"amount\": \"1/2\"}, {\"id\": 3, \"name\": \"salt\", \"unit\": \"Teaspoon\", \"amount\": \"3/4\"}, {\"id\": 4, \"name\": \"unsalted butter, melted and cooled\", \"unit\": \"cup\", \"amount\": \"1/2\"}, {\"id\": 5, \"name\": \"light brown sugar, packed\", \"unit\": \"cup\", \"amount\": \"1/2\"}, {\"id\": 6, \"name\": \"granulated sugar\", \"unit\": \"cup\", \"amount\": \"1/3\"}, {\"id\": 7, \"name\": \"vanill