(100,"Beef Rice Bowl","","00:00:00","00:20:00","2","easy","[\"Slice the beef into thin, bite sized pieces.\", \"Heat a skillet and place the beef slices in an even layer. No need to add oil. Cook for 3-4 minutes on each side until slightly browned, then remove to a paper towel lined plate and set aside.\", \"In a small bowl, whisk together the Soyaki and honey. Then add the sauce to a pan and heat until simmering, about 5 minutes. Lower the heat and add the pork belly slices, coating them in the Soyaki-Honey sauce. Heat for 2-3 minutes.\", \"Bring a pot of water to a boil, then using a ladle, gently drop the eggs into the boiling water and cook for 6-6 1/2 minutes.\", \"Fill a bowl with cold water and ice and as soon as the eggs are done cooking, place them immediately into the ice bath for at least 5 minutes, then peel and slice in half. The eggs should be slightly runny.\", \"Microwave the pouch (or pouches) of rice for 3 minutes.\", \"Assemble the bowls by dividing the rice, then serve the beef on top, and the eggs. Top with sliced green onions, sriracha-mayo, and a soft boiled egg, if desired.\"]","2024-03-04 15:39:38","b6f32b03-9d03-4ff9-8c06-08932e3d7940","{\"key\": \"8c52c5b6-9d07-4831-a5be-ef6c390fdced-1xej19.jpeg\", \"url\": \"https://utfs.io/f/8c52c5b6-9d07-4831-a5be-ef6c390fdced-1xej19.jpeg\", \"name\": \"IMG_8988.jpeg\", \"size\": 1896174}",NULL,"2024-03-09 19:08:16","[{\"id\": 0, \"name\": \"Beef\", \"note\": \"sliced\", \"unit\": \"Ounce\", \"amount\": \"12\"}, {\"id\": 1, \"name\": \"Soyaki\", \"unit\": \"tablespoon\", \"amount\": \"4\"}, {\"id\": 2, \"name\": \"Honey\", \"unit\": \"tablespoon\", \"amount\": \"3\"}, {\"id\": 3, \"name\": \"Eggs\", \"note\": \"soft boiled\", \"unit\": \"whole\", \"amount\": \"2\"}, {\"id\": 4, \"name\": \"Jasmine Rice\", \"unit\": \"pouche\", \"amount\": \"1-2\"}, {\"id\": 5, \"name\": \"Green Onion\", \"note\": \"optional\", \"unit\": \"\", \"amount\": \"\"}, {\"id\": 6, \"name\": \"Black Garlic\", \"note\": \"optiona